data.description: This awesome custom built home features 5 bedrooms, 5 bathrooms, larger living room with floor to ceiling windows with great view, super kitchen with granite counter tops, tons of built ins including refrigerators, dishwashers, walk out patio from kitchen and master bedroom and basement. master bath has air flow tub with , walk in shower, Also has a spa, 2 fireplaces, circle drive that is covered, sprinkler system, Located on 3.8 acres in Altamira. This is an awesome home.
